Package: teachingApps
Type: Package
Title: Build, Update, and Share Shiny Apps - Quickly And Easily
Version: 0.6
Date: 2017-2-7
Author: Jason K. Freels
Maintainer: Jason K. Freels <auburngrads@live.com>
Description: Instantly create shiny app templates and app calling functions 
    for use in R packages.  Manage large collections of shiny apps from one 
    location.  Update the structure or appearance of apps on the fly.  Nest 
    small apps together to create complex 'storyteller' apps. Publish stand-
    alone apps or embed in rmarkdown documents with app calling functions.
    Includes over 100 shiny apps and shiny gadgets for analyzing data and   
    teaching various concepts (statistics and R programming). 
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: shiny,shinyAce,shinythemes,DT,devtools,graphics,metricsgraphics,
          utils,knitr,leaflet,threejs,d3heatmap,plotly,htmlwidgets,dygraphs,
          networkD3,diagram,DiagrammeR,visNetwork,scales,data.table,miniUI,
          shinydashboard,d3Network,ggplot2,actuar,markdown,stats,shinygadgets
NeedsCompilation: no
Archs: i386, x64
Suggests: testthat, rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 6.0.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
